a.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #666666;">-No te obsesiones, ya sabes que es una cosa de genética, quierete y aceptate.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #666666;">Ahora dime, que es más saludable y sexy?</p>\r\n<p style="color: #666666;"><a href="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/healthy1.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-315" src="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/healthy1-300x231.jpg" alt="healthy1" width="300" height="231" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="color: #666666;"></p>\r\n<p style="color: #666666;"><a href="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Bonitadas-Thigh-gap-Fitsugar3.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-317" src="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Bonitadas-Thigh-gap-Fitsugar3-300x300.jpg" alt="Bonitadas-Thigh gap-Fitsugar3" width="300" height="300" /></a></p>', 'LA OBSESIÓN CON EL "THIG GAP"', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '314-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-04 21:30:59', '2014-08-04 21:30:59', '', 314, 'http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/314-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
