ial, representando lo que realmente significa “Be more Human” que es superar retos, convertirnos en mejores líderes, convertirnos en seres humanos más capaces y mejores. Aplaudo a esta marca que logra identificar a miles de Fitness Lovers en el mundo y que se reinventó con un concepto nuevo, único y moderno.       <a href="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/maxresdefault-1.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-685 size-full" src="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/maxresdefault-1.jpg" alt="maxresdefault (1)" width="1200" height="675" /></a> <a href="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/reebok-be-more-human-hed-2015.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-687 size-full" src="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/reebok-be-more-human-hed-2015.jpg" alt="reebok-be-more-human-hed-2015" width="1200" height="673" /></a> <a href="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/RBK_Be_more-_human_1200x630_fb.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-686 size-full" src="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/RBK_Be_more-_human_1200x630_fb.jpg" alt="RBK_Be_more-_human_1200x630_fb" width="1200" height="630" /></a> <a href="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Screenshot-2015-01-28-16.27.52.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-689 size-full" src="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Screenshot-2015-01-28-16.27.52.png" alt="Screenshot-2015-01-28-16.27.52" width="1200" height="675" /></a> <a href="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/reebok-launches-be-more-human-campaign-1.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-688 size-full" src="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/reebok-launches-be-more-human-campai