 que si alguien esta pensando en vivirla, no lo dude y hágalo ya, yo lo recomiendo a ojos cerrados. Espero en mi corazón volver.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/DSC_0131-copy.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-753 size-full" src="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/DSC_0131-copy.jpg" alt="DSC_0131 copy" width="1200" height="745" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/DSC_0114-copy.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-751 size-full" src="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/DSC_0114-copy.jpg" alt="DSC_0114 copy" width="1200" height="795" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/121.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-743 size-full" src="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/121.jpg" alt="12" width="1200" height="900" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/DSC_0118-copy.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-752 size-full" src="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/DSC_0118-copy.jpg" alt="DSC_0118 copy" width="1200" height="795" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1509153_10152917974042578_5561100524852016495_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-744 size-full" src="http://local.mediatrends/_Chicachic/htdocs-new/app/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1509153_10152917974042578_5561100524852016495_n.jpg" alt="1509153_10152917974042578_5561100524852016495_n" width="1200" height="1200" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r